1
00:02:05,792 --> 00:02:07,792
Shit!
该死

2
00:02:13,802 --> 00:02:15,802
Did I hurt myself?
受伤了

3
00:02:15,802 --> 00:02:18,722
My God - blood!
出血了

4
00:02:52,842 --> 00:02:54,842
- Everything okay, Marcel? - No.
你还好吗

5
00:02:54,842 --> 00:02:58,842
What do you think, with the middle of my face smashed in?
我的脸刚才受伤了

6
00:03:03,852 --> 00:03:06,228
Red wine.
要红酒

7
00:03:41,892 --> 00:03:45,902
These glasses are smaller than a drunkard's dreams.
这不是干净的杯子

8
00:03:45,902 --> 00:03:50,063
- Any luck with the publisher? - No, the swine!
出版社怎么样 说我的戏曲太长了

9
00:03:50,063 --> 00:03:53,066
He said it was too long and demanded cuts,
也不给我定金  只是叫我写短一点

10
00:03:53,066 --> 00:03:55,912
but with no promises and no advance - the lout!
混蛋

11
00:03:55,912 --> 00:03:58,912
- Why not let me read it? - You?
能给我看看吗 你

12
00:03:58,912 --> 00:03:59,912
Yes, me.
是的

13
00:03:59,912 --> 00:04:02,826
You can read?
你识字吗

14
00:04:02,912 --> 00:04:03,912
Are you kidding?
可以看懂

15
00:04:03,912 --> 00:04:07,312
I finished third grade in Mongéo before coming to Paris.
我在小学的时候已经学过

16
00:04:07,312 --> 00:04:09,922
I'll read it at bedtime.
我想在入睡之前念

17
00:04:09,922 --> 00:04:11,922
Why not?
好吧我借给你

18
00:04:11,922 --> 00:04:14,922
You'll give me the people's appraisal
看完后告诉我你的感想

19
00:04:14,922 --> 00:04:18,922
and put the publishers to shame.
希望你能看出出版商  没能看出的东西

20
00:04:25,307 --> 00:04:29,932
<i>The Avenger - A Play in 21 Acts</i> by Marcel Marx
"复仇者"21幕剧

21
00:06:22,052 --> 00:06:24,968
EVICTION NOTICE
马上搬出去

22
00:06:49,082 --> 00:06:53,082
Good morning, Monsieur Marcel. Have you forgotten that today is the eighth?
马歇尔先生  我们已经说好8日退房吧

23
00:06:53,082 --> 00:06:57,082
Already? How time rushes on!
这么快就到时间了吗

24
00:06:58,092 --> 00:07:00,092
You're a bit slow in vacating the premises.
请搬出去

25
00:07:00,092 --> 00:07:02,923
It's already 11:30.
已经11点半了  下一位住户到了

26
00:07:02,923 --> 00:07:07,102
The new tenant may arrive at any moment. Allow me to find a moving van.
请帮我叫一下出租车

27
00:07:07,102 --> 00:07:09,095
By all means!
谢谢

28
00:07:09,095 --> 00:07:13,099
But there's one little formality to see to first:
但之前还有点事情要做

29
00:07:14,017 --> 00:07:18,112
your three months' back rent. Would you mind? - Of course not.
你还没有交3个月的房租

30
00:07:18,112 --> 00:07:23,112
Then kindly step into my office, so I may give you a receipt.
我会付清的 如果你到事务所  我会给你开单

31
00:07:23,112 --> 00:07:26,029
- When I return. - Why not now?
回来之后马上过去 现在马上

32
00:07:26,029 --> 00:07:30,112
I must go to the bank. I don't carry a sum like that on me.
不去银行就没有钱给你

33
00:07:33,122 --> 00:07:36,132
I see. No cash.
那就没办法了

34
00:07:36,132 --> 00:07:39,793
Then allow me to relieve you of that little burden
等你回来之前  我会替你保管这些东西

35
00:07:39,793 --> 00:07:44,142
so it doesn't tire you. You think I'd carry off my belongings in a bag?
如果这里面  有贵重东西怎么办

36
00:07:44,142 --> 00:07:46,142
Those are the rules.
这是规矩

37
00:07:46,142 --> 00:07:50,804
You're not to remove so much as a single hair until the rent is paid.
付清房租之前  你别想拿走任何东西

38
00:07:50,929 --> 00:07:52,931
There's no hair in here,
里面是我的衬衫

39
00:07:52,931 --> 00:07:58,152
just shirts I'm taking to the laundry next door to the bank, just steps from here.
我想拿到银行隔壁的洗衣房

40
00:07:58,152 --> 00:08:00,152
Please do not misunderstand me,
你把我当成傻瓜吗

41
00:08:00,152 --> 00:08:02,857
but certain unfortunate experiences
租房子的人不可信  这是我长年的经验

42
00:08:02,857 --> 00:08:05,652
have shattered my faith in tenants.
租房子的人不可信  这是我长年的经验

43
00:08:06,162 --> 00:08:10,152
Hugo had best accompany you to the bank.
尤高会跟你一起去银行

44
00:08:15,172 --> 00:08:18,498
摩勒克福银行

45
00:08:18,498 --> 00:08:22,172
See this man? He's been casing this bank for three days.
这家伙一直  在银行周围转来转去

46
00:08:22,172 --> 00:08:26,182
I live across the street. His accomplice is around the corner in an Alfa Romeo,
还有一个就在那里  他一直装作看报纸

47
00:08:26,182 --> 00:08:28,182
reading <i>Le Monde -</i> upside down.
在车上看哨

48
00:08:28,182 --> 00:08:30,102
I only wish to do my duty.
因为我的所有财产都在

49
00:08:30,102 --> 00:08:32,182
My life's savings are in this bank.
这个银行所以我向你告发

50
00:08:32,182 --> 00:08:36,182
What do you suppose is in his bag?
请搜查他的包

51
00:08:58,212 --> 00:09:00,212
Has my apartment been vacated?
房子已经空出来了吧

52
00:09:00,212 --> 00:09:04,222
Not yet, Monsieur Schaunard, but very soon.
我马上收拾好

53
00:09:04,222 --> 00:09:08,222
The previous tenant, a writer, has gone to get a moving van.
之前住过的人把箱子  放在我这里就走了

54
00:09:08,222 --> 00:09:12,232
In the meantime, you may leave your furniture outside.
我帮你搬东西到走廊

55
00:09:12,232 --> 00:09:16,222
I'm afraid. If it rains, my furniture will be damaged.
如果下雨家具会潮湿

56
00:09:22,242 --> 00:09:25,242
You will forgive me if I ask your profession.
你是做什么工作的

57
00:09:25,242 --> 00:09:29,232
You neglected to indicate that on the lease.
在合同上没有

58
00:09:31,242 --> 00:09:36,076
Leave the piano here and return at once to my old lodgings
钢琴就这么放着 到公寓  把高档家私搬过来吧

59
00:09:36,076 --> 00:09:42,242
for the rest of my priceless furnishings and works of art.
还有我的艺术品

60
00:09:51,174 --> 00:09:56,012
Henri, from the Ministry of War. It just arrived by courier.
是国防大臣的信 刚刚到

61
00:09:56,012 --> 00:09:58,262
The Ministry of War.
国防大臣

62
00:10:00,272 --> 00:10:03,478
It must be the pension
是我期待已久的  养老金领取书

63
00:10:03,478 --> 00:10:09,282
that I've been waiting for all these years. At last some recognition of my achievements.
终于可以拿到钱了

64
00:10:09,282 --> 00:10:13,863
<i>Dear Monsieur Bernard, courtesy demands that I inform you</i>
"贝尔那先生" "我把我的不幸遭遇告诉你"

65
00:10:13,863 --> 00:10:19,292
<i>of the unfortunate predicament I find myself in</i> <i>that prevents me at this time from observing the custom</i>
"这次之后"

66
00:10:19,292 --> 00:10:22,302
<i>requiring that rent be paid, especially when it's due.</i>
"不会再付房租了"

67
00:10:22,302 --> 00:10:25,458
<i>Until this morning I had hoped</i>
"到今天早上为止  我都想付清房租"

68
00:10:25,458 --> 00:10:28,302
<i>to honor this lo very day by paying my rent</i> - <i>ah, delusion!</i>
"到今天早上为止  我都想付清房租"

69
00:10:28,302 --> 00:10:31,302
<i>As I slept cradled in false certainty, misfortune -</i>
"但和我的期待相反"

70
00:10:31,302 --> 00:10:35,312
Ananke <i>in Greek - dashed my hopes.</i>
"我的这些想法被打破了"

71
00:10:35,312 --> 00:10:38,312
<i>Certain sizable sums I expected did not materialize,</i>
"我没有钱"

72
00:10:38,312 --> 00:10:42,322
<i>but our beautiful France and I will see better days - have no doubt of that.</i>
"我相信幸运之神  会降临在法国和我身上"

73
00:10:42,322 --> 00:10:47,322
<i>The moment we do, I shall hasten to inform you of it</i>
"有了收入之后我会马上通知你"

74
00:10:47,322 --> 00:10:51,332
<i>and to remove from my lodgings my precious possessions,</i>
"再取回留在房子里的  我的贵重品"

75
00:10:51,332 --> 00:10:55,155
<i>which I leave to your safekeeping and to that of the law,</i>
那之前先让您  和法律来保护它吧

76
00:10:55,155 --> 00:10:58,332
<i>which restrains you from selling them for one year.</i>
"不要在一年之内  处理那些东西"

77
00:10:58,332 --> 00:11:02,120
<i>Until then you are at liberty to use</i>
"那之前请随便使用房间"

78
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:07,342
<i>the luxurious lodgings in which I have resided.</i> <i>In affirmation of my consent, I hereby affix my signature.</i>
"我在这里把这件事告诉您"

79
00:11:07,342 --> 00:11:11,332
<i>Marcel Marx.</i>
"马歇尔·马科斯"

80
00:11:39,372 --> 00:11:43,372
- Two half orders of trout. - Yes, sir.
给我半份鳟鱼

81
00:11:48,382 --> 00:11:50,382
That's a strange order.
奇怪的要求

82
00:11:50,382 --> 00:11:54,392
On the contrary. This method yields on average
那是经过计算之后得出来的

83
00:11:54,392 --> 00:11:58,468
a quarter more than ordering a full portion.
这比要一份量更多

84
00:12:10,412 --> 00:12:11,412
Where is my order?
我的呢

85
00:12:11,412 --> 00:12:16,069
I'm afraid this gentleman got the last trout.
鳟鱼料理已经不做了

86
00:12:20,422 --> 00:12:24,422
May I invite you to partake of this course with me?
不介意和我分吧

87
00:12:24,422 --> 00:12:27,422
I would not deprive you of what is yours, sir.
我不想夺取你的食物

88
00:12:27,422 --> 00:12:32,168
Then you'd deprive me of the pleasure of expressing my goodwill?
你想无视我的好意吗

89
00:12:32,293 --> 00:12:36,422
In that case, sir...
那我就不客气了

90
00:12:42,345 --> 00:12:44,442
Permit me to refrain from serving you the head.
鱼头我吃

91
00:12:44,442 --> 00:12:47,442
That I couldn't allow.
这对你不公平

92
00:12:47,442 --> 00:12:50,452
For if the head is man's noblest appendage,
人类的大脑中  需要一些养分

93
00:12:50,452 --> 00:12:55,108
it's the most unpleasant part of a trout.
鳟鱼的头可以满足这些需要

94
00:12:56,452 --> 00:13:00,405
Two heads! This trout is bicephalic,
有两个头双头  原本是希腊语

95
00:13:00,405 --> 00:13:07,120
a word which comes from the Greek and means... precisely that.
怎么会有双头的鳟鱼

96
00:13:08,462 --> 00:13:13,462
Nevertheless, I harbor no regrets about eating this phenomenon.
吃一些奇形怪状的鱼  已经很普遍

97
00:13:21,384 --> 00:13:23,482
The sauce was delicious.
真是好吃的料理

98
00:13:23,482 --> 00:13:27,482
True. It was prepared in the province of Béarn,
我也这么认为

99
00:13:27,482 --> 00:13:30,492
and its fine reputation is richly deserved.
这里都是些有名的料理

100
00:13:30,492 --> 00:13:34,480
You seem very learned. You're not from here?
你怎么会对这里这么熟悉  是巴黎人吗

101
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:37,492
No. I come from Albania
我是阿尔巴尼亚人

102
00:13:37,492 --> 00:13:41,321
and have lived in Paris only three years now.
住在巴黎已经有3年了

103
00:13:41,321 --> 00:13:43,502
Yet you've already mastered our language.
讲法语真棒

104
00:13:43,502 --> 00:13:48,502
My nursemaid was French, from Barcelona.
我的乳娘是从巴塞罗那  来的法国人

105
00:13:48,502 --> 00:13:52,512
My name is Rodolfo, and I'm a painter.
我叫罗德洛夫是画家

106
00:13:52,512 --> 00:13:54,512
Marcel Marx, writer.
我是作家马科斯

107
00:13:54,512 --> 00:13:57,512
May I offer you a bottle of wine?
我想请你喝酒

108
00:13:57,512 --> 00:13:59,522
Only on one condition:
我有条件

109
00:13:59,522 --> 00:14:03,522
that I see to the coffee and the rest.
咖啡由我自己拿

110
00:14:03,522 --> 00:14:05,522
As a painter, don't you think
作为画家你有什么意见

111
00:14:05,522 --> 00:14:09,766
that Malevich's <i>Black</i> Square
就像马雷奇  改变绘画的方向一样

112
00:14:09,932 --> 00:14:16,532
is as lethal a blow to painting as the school of Vienna - Schoenberg, Berg, Webern, and the rest - is to music?
肖恩等流派的人

113
00:14:16,532 --> 00:14:20,532
- I agree entirely. - Let's go.
改变了音乐 要走了

114
00:14:32,455 --> 00:14:36,793
I live just around the corner. We may continue our discussion there.
我住在附近  到我那里继续说吧

115
00:14:40,562 --> 00:14:45,551
“I floated down impassive rivers, unguided now by bargemen's hands.
"我喝醉了  坐在船上在河上行驶"

116
00:14:45,562 --> 00:14:48,304
Howling natives had hauled them up for targets
"不幸的是  船被印第安人打沉了"

117
00:14:48,304 --> 00:14:52,975
and nailed them naked to painted stakes.” Beautiful stuff, Rimbaud.
是兰博

118
00:14:53,976 --> 00:14:58,314
He and Verlaine argued vehemently about -

119
00:14:58,481 --> 00:15:01,401
Anyway, come inside.

120
00:15:02,582 --> 00:15:04,582
This is where I live.
这里就是我家

121
00:15:04,582 --> 00:15:06,572
谢谢

122
00:15:12,537 --> 00:15:17,708
Strange. The key's in the lock, though I put it in my pocket this morning -
糟了  我把钥匙放在房间窗户上

123
00:15:21,212 --> 00:15:23,602
where it remains even now.
你先在这里等着

124
00:15:23,602 --> 00:15:27,592
It's witchcraft! Two keys.
你变魔法了  有两个钥匙

125
00:15:29,612 --> 00:15:33,602
Someone's playing the violin. These aren't my lodgings.
是钢琴声音真奇怪

126
00:15:54,632 --> 00:15:56,632
May I help you?
有什么事吗

127
00:15:56,632 --> 00:16:00,642
I was mistaken. This isn't my apartment.
我还以为这是我的房子

128
00:16:00,642 --> 00:16:04,088
I beg your pardon on my friend's behalf.
失礼了他喝醉了

129
00:16:04,088 --> 00:16:07,925
He's exceptionally drunk. Wait, this is my place.
我还以为是我的房子...

130
00:16:07,925 --> 00:16:12,642
That's my finery!
那是我的衣服

131
00:16:13,652 --> 00:16:15,652
And what's this?
这是什么

132
00:16:15,652 --> 00:16:20,271
My Turkish slippers, given to me by beloved hands!
这是朋友送给我的拖鞋

133
00:16:23,662 --> 00:16:27,672
“Marcel Marx is hereby obligated to vacate the premises
"马歇尔·马科斯先生  到8日正午之前"

134
00:16:27,672 --> 00:16:30,672
by noon on February eighth...”
"请马上退房"

135
00:16:30,672 --> 00:16:33,993
Am I not the Marcel Marx
我就是被他赶走的  马歇尔·马科斯

136
00:16:33,993 --> 00:16:37,580
whom the landlord evicted?
我听说过

137
00:16:37,580 --> 00:16:41,792
The situation is as follows. By law
法律上这里是我的房间

138
00:16:41,792 --> 00:16:47,692
the premises are mine, for you were evicted, and I paid in advance.
你被房东赶走  我就搬进来住了

139
00:16:47,692 --> 00:16:50,692
Yes, for the premises, but not the furnishings.
房子是你的没错  但这些家具就不是

140
00:16:50,692 --> 00:16:53,429
If I pay up, I may remove them legally -
即使没有交房租  家具也是我的

141
00:16:53,429 --> 00:17:00,019
or even illegally, if it were possible. Thus you have furnishings but no lodgings,
你可以拿回家具  但没有房子

142
00:17:00,144 --> 00:17:02,702
and I have lodgings but no furniture. - Precisely.
我不会让你住进来

143
00:17:02,702 --> 00:17:04,702
I like the apartment.
这里真是不错的房子

144
00:17:04,702 --> 00:17:07,712
And I've never liked it more. - Pardon?
是很脏的房子

145
00:17:07,712 --> 00:17:10,712
Never as much as now, and I know what I'm saying.
但给你住就有点可惜了

146
00:17:10,712 --> 00:17:14,408
What do you say we lubricate this explanation?
慢点说吧

147
00:17:25,722 --> 00:17:27,732
What an amazing pipe you have.
真是不错的茬子

148
00:17:27,732 --> 00:17:32,732
I have an even more handsome one for use in high society.
我在上流社会的时候  拿着都是名贵的东西

149
00:17:32,732 --> 00:17:35,722
Would you care to try it? - With pleasure.
你试一下 谢谢

150
00:17:36,472 --> 00:17:39,742
You appear to be a man of musical bent.
你是音乐迷吗

151
00:17:39,742 --> 00:17:41,742
A composer.
我是作曲家

152
00:17:41,742 --> 00:17:44,742
I'm writing a piece called
现在正准备新的曲子

153
00:17:44,742 --> 00:17:49,443
“The Influence of Blue on the Arts.”
是叫做  "蓝色对艺术的影响"的作品

154
00:20:31,522 --> 00:20:34,912
- I can't see anyone just now. - Why not?
现在不行 为什么

155
00:20:34,912 --> 00:20:36,986
Good morning.
中午好

156
00:20:37,922 --> 00:20:39,922
Good morning, mademoiselle.
马托摩洁丽

157
00:20:39,922 --> 00:20:43,033
- There's my answer. - I understand.
这就是原因 知道了

158
00:20:43,922 --> 00:20:47,705
All the same, perhaps you might lend me 1,000 francs.
借我100法郎

159
00:20:47,705 --> 00:20:49,932
I'm all out of paint,
涂料用完了

160
00:20:49,932 --> 00:20:52,932
and I can't complete my masterpiece.
我完成不了  正在创作中的画

161
00:20:52,932 --> 00:20:56,714
You're asking a lot. I'm broke at the moment.
我也是个穷光蛋

162
00:20:56,714 --> 00:20:58,942
Couldn't you borrow it from the girl?
你跟那个女人说说看

163
00:20:58,942 --> 00:21:02,942
I couldn't do that. We just met yesterday.
不行她是昨天才认识的

164
00:21:02,942 --> 00:21:06,223
- And Schaunard? - No one's seen him all week.
肖纳罗呢 这一周一直没见到他  回去吧

165
00:21:06,223 --> 00:21:07,683
Good-bye.
肖纳罗呢 这一周一直没见到他  回去吧

166
00:21:15,858 --> 00:21:17,735
Where are you going?
你去哪里

167
00:21:17,735 --> 00:21:21,962
To your place... to collect what you owe me.
我想要回借给你的钱

168
00:21:21,962 --> 00:21:24,867
You won't find me at home.
真遗憾

169
00:21:25,701 --> 00:21:29,962
I can't pay you back today. I'm waiting for a girl.
今天有约会所以不能还给你

170
00:21:31,665 --> 00:21:35,962
But you can pawn my ring.
你先拿着这个戒指

171
00:21:36,982 --> 00:21:38,982
There she is.
来了

172
00:21:38,982 --> 00:21:40,972
Beat it.
快点消失

173
00:21:55,002 --> 00:21:58,234
What if she comes back to you?
如果卖掉戒指  你妻子会难过的

174
00:21:58,234 --> 00:22:00,569
You'd no longer have the ring.
如果卖掉戒指  你妻子会难过的

175
00:22:01,002 --> 00:22:03,781
She won't come back.
她不会再回来了

176
00:22:03,781 --> 00:22:07,326
She ran off with an American.
她和开卡迪拉克的  美国人跑掉了

177
00:22:07,326 --> 00:22:11,012
He had a Cadillac. It's a shame about the children.
留下孩子们

178
00:22:11,012 --> 00:22:13,749
She left them with me,
因为没有钱  我无法买东西给孩子们吃

179
00:22:13,749 --> 00:22:17,022
and I don't have enough to feed them.
因为没有钱  我无法买东西给孩子们吃

180
00:22:17,022 --> 00:22:20,756
They cry out from hunger in the night.
晚上因为肚饿哭个不停

181
00:22:20,756 --> 00:22:22,508
How old are they?
孩子几岁了

182
00:22:22,508 --> 00:22:25,094
Fourteen... nine...
14岁小的9岁

183
00:22:25,094 --> 00:22:28,347
seven... six... three... two...
还有7岁的6岁的  3岁的和1岁的

184
00:22:28,347 --> 00:22:31,032
one... and the youngest is just six months.
最小的只有6个月

185
00:22:31,032 --> 00:22:33,032
So many!
真是人山人海啊

186
00:22:33,032 --> 00:22:37,042
We were young and in love.
是冲动造成的

187
00:22:37,042 --> 00:22:39,275
It was spring.
现在还年轻

188
00:24:11,132 --> 00:24:13,786
You look strange.
怎么样

189
00:24:13,994 --> 00:24:16,132
What's the matter?
什么

190
00:24:16,872 --> 00:24:19,541
I think I have fallen in love.
我想谈恋爱

191
00:24:20,142 --> 00:24:22,142
With whom?
有目标吗

192
00:24:22,142 --> 00:24:26,507
I don't know... but she's sitting over there.
是不知名的女人  正坐在对面

193
00:24:27,152 --> 00:24:29,718
She's not bad-looking.
不错的女人

194
00:24:30,152 --> 00:24:32,763
Why don't you do something?
诱惑看看

195
00:24:34,162 --> 00:24:37,059
What if she rejects me?
如果被拒绝

196
00:24:37,162 --> 00:24:41,152
I'd never get over it.
我就没面子了

197
00:24:42,162 --> 00:24:45,172
It's our custom in Albania to first -
在我故乡阿尔巴尼亚

198
00:24:45,172 --> 00:24:47,162
You stay here.
看我的

199
00:24:47,987 --> 00:24:52,172
I'll go speak to her on your behalf.
我帮你试试看

200
00:24:52,172 --> 00:24:56,787
I will awaken in her heart a passion...
在她的心中点燃一股火焰

201
00:24:57,413 --> 00:25:01,625
for you. I will lie
用甜言蜜语

202
00:25:01,750 --> 00:25:03,752
shamelessly.

203
00:25:10,092 --> 00:25:12,192
Good evening.
你好

204
00:25:12,192 --> 00:25:17,433
See that man over there? He is in love with you.
坐在对面的男人看上了你

205
00:25:22,521 --> 00:25:25,202
But so am I.
我也是

206
00:25:57,014 --> 00:26:00,059
Excuse me. Can I help you?
怎么了

207
00:26:00,184 --> 00:26:01,977
I fell asleep.
已经睡着了

208
00:26:01,977 --> 00:26:03,228
Where are you going?
你是访客

209
00:26:03,228 --> 00:26:04,605
Nowhere.
我是从乡下过来的

210
00:26:04,605 --> 00:26:07,900
I arrived in town, but my girlfriend isn't in.
来探望朋友但她不在

211
00:26:07,900 --> 00:26:12,071
I was to stay with her. It's no use waiting.
等了也没用还有3年的牢要坐

212
00:26:12,071 --> 00:26:15,199
She was taken to prison, for three years.
等了也没用还有3年的牢要坐

213
00:26:22,272 --> 00:26:24,272
What am I going to do now?
真为难

214
00:26:24,272 --> 00:26:28,629
I arrived today from Rouen. I don't know anyone here.
我在巴黎没有认识人

215
00:26:29,272 --> 00:26:33,884
If you like... I live next door.
我是她的邻居你进来休息吧

216
00:26:34,282 --> 00:26:38,180
Tell me: Are you a proper French gentleman?
你是绅士一样的法国人吧

217
00:26:38,180 --> 00:26:39,431
No.
是没错

218
00:26:39,431 --> 00:26:45,292
I mean, yes... but I'm not French. I'm Albanian.
我是阿尔巴尼亚人

219
00:26:45,292 --> 00:26:47,981
That Will do.
好吧

220
00:27:22,332 --> 00:27:25,227
I'm going now and taking the dog with me.
我带狗出去

221
00:27:25,332 --> 00:27:28,332
He sometimes makes noise at night due to nightmares.
你睡觉的时候狗会吠个不停

222
00:27:28,332 --> 00:27:32,342
But why? I can sleep on the sofa.
为什么出去  我在沙发睡就可以了

223
00:27:32,342 --> 00:27:35,320
It's too hard for a bed.
在沙发睡觉不会舒服

224
00:27:35,320 --> 00:27:41,243
And besides... I'm hot-blooded, and you are very beautiful.
而且我动作很快你又这么漂亮

225
00:27:41,352 --> 00:27:44,580
- Where will you go? - To a friend's.
那你去哪里 就在附近的朋友家

226
00:27:44,580 --> 00:27:46,582
He lives close by.
那你去哪里 就在附近的朋友家

227
00:27:48,352 --> 00:27:53,046
Sleep peacefully. I'll be back in the morning.
慢慢睡吧  明天早上我才回来

228
00:28:37,402 --> 00:28:39,676
Baudelaire.
波特里

229
00:28:59,422 --> 00:29:03,422
"安里·穆杰鲁"

230
00:29:21,452 --> 00:30:26,512
“I have gone to seek lodgings. Thank you for your kindness. Mimi.” Where's your black coat?
"我正在找住的地方  谢谢你的款待眯米" 黑色上衣呢

231
00:30:26,512 --> 00:30:28,744
Can't you see?
就这个

232
00:30:30,522 --> 00:30:32,789
You've ruined it.
已经弄脏了

233
00:30:33,040 --> 00:30:34,958
I'm lost.

234
00:30:36,902 --> 00:30:38,902
I've been summoned by Gassot, the newspaper czar.
我和新闻王见面

235
00:30:38,902 --> 00:30:42,632
He's founding a fashion magazine, <i>The Sash of Iris,</i>
我面试一个新增杂志的编辑

236
00:30:42,632 --> 00:30:47,912
and plans to make me editor in chief. If I show up in this getup, he may change his mind.
就这样去的话肯定不行

237
00:30:47,912 --> 00:30:50,912
You can't accept his offer anyway.
那种事情还是早点别想

238
00:30:50,912 --> 00:30:54,922
Gassot is a supporter of the right.
卡索是右翼分子

239
00:30:54,922 --> 00:30:57,647
Your principles won't allow you to eat bread
你想帮榨取民脂民膏的  人做事吗

240
00:30:57,647 --> 00:31:02,861
bathed in the sweat of the people. - You're mistaken. He's in the left flank of the right wing in Parliament.
不他在右翼中也倾向左派

241
00:31:02,861 --> 00:31:05,280
Just yesterday he voted for widows' pensions.
他提倡遗孤补偿金  而且还认识很多大人物

242
00:31:05,280 --> 00:31:09,284
Besides, he knows influential people whom I'll convince to commission
这是你们两个出名的好机会

243
00:31:09,284 --> 00:31:16,958
compositions from you and portraits from Rodolfo. That changes everything. What time's your meeting?
那还可以  你什么时候和他见面

244
00:31:18,627 --> 00:31:20,932
At 5100.
5点

245
00:31:22,402 --> 00:31:25,717
There's no time to lose.
那就快点吧

246
00:31:26,692 --> 00:31:28,832
I can polish my shoes black
把鞋子涂成黑色

247
00:31:28,832 --> 00:31:31,973
so no one will notice
那样的话  就算两边不一样也不易发现

248
00:31:31,973 --> 00:31:34,935
that one is round-toed and the other pointed.
那样的话  就算两边不一样也不易发现

249
00:31:36,332 --> 00:31:39,481
I need a black coat!
我需要件黑色上衣

250
00:31:39,481 --> 00:31:43,592
I'd give ten years of my life and my right hand for one.
如果不想点办法

251
00:31:43,592 --> 00:31:46,602
- Is Rodolfo the painter in? - That's me.
洛特勒夫在吗 就是我

252
00:31:46,602 --> 00:31:50,033
My cousin recommends your reasonably priced portraits.
你的肖像画好像很受欢迎

253
00:31:50,033 --> 00:31:54,602
I'm told they're very good likenesses. More accurate than photographs.
比书上的更好

254
00:31:54,602 --> 00:31:57,707
He's very talented.
学校还让他过去教学生

255
00:31:57,707 --> 00:32:01,612
He won every award at school. My son won an award, and he's only seven.
我儿子已经7岁  在学校也拿过奖

256
00:32:01,612 --> 00:32:03,612
A talented child.
真是神童

257
00:32:03,612 --> 00:32:05,612
This portrait you want, Monsieur...
你要那幅画

258
00:32:05,612 --> 00:32:09,622
Blancheron, from Nantes. I'm a sugar producer.
我是砂糖工厂老板佛兰修罗

259
00:32:09,622 --> 00:32:11,622
I've even written books on the subject.
而且写过关于砂糖的著作

260
00:32:11,622 --> 00:32:15,622
I'd like a medium-sized portrait.
我要一个很大的画

261
00:32:15,622 --> 00:32:18,632
Like that one. Who is that of?
是谁的肖像呢

262
00:32:18,632 --> 00:32:19,632
My mother.
是我母亲

263
00:32:19,632 --> 00:32:22,632
How much would one of that size cost?
那么大的多少钱

264
00:32:22,632 --> 00:32:24,632
Between 1,000 and 1,200 francs,
1000到1200法郎

265
00:32:24,632 --> 00:32:27,642
depending on whether your hands show.
这个价钱很合理

266
00:32:27,642 --> 00:32:29,642
- My cousin said 500. - It depends on the season.
500怎么样

267
00:32:29,642 --> 00:32:32,642
Paint prices vary with the season.
因为画具的价钱也会改变

268
00:32:32,642 --> 00:32:36,652
- Interesting. Just like sugar. - Precisely.
和砂糖市场一样吗 没错

269
00:32:36,652 --> 00:32:38,652
- Paint me one for 1,000 francs. - You're making a mistake.
那就1000法郎

270
00:32:38,652 --> 00:32:44,838
For 200 more, he'll paint your hands holding your book on sugar.
如果再给多200法郎 可以把你的书加到画里面

271
00:32:44,838 --> 00:32:47,662
You simply must do it. - Would that look good?
就这样定了

272
00:32:47,662 --> 00:32:50,385
Exceptionally good.
就在你家里画吗

273
00:32:50,385 --> 00:32:52,846
Is the portrait for your home?
在我的寝室画

274
00:32:52,846 --> 00:32:57,662
Yes, the living room. Then you must be in a dressing gown.
那就穿便装最好了

275
00:32:58,672 --> 00:33:01,313
Please sit in this chair.
请坐

276
00:33:02,672 --> 00:33:05,275
Take off your coat.
换衣服

277
00:33:08,682 --> 00:33:10,682
I don't have a dressing gown with me.
我没有便装

278
00:33:10,682 --> 00:33:15,202
Don't worry. My friend will lend you his.
不用担心穿着这个就可以

279
00:33:23,692 --> 00:33:28,548
Marcel, please hang up the gentleman's coat.
马歇尔把上衣挂好

280
00:33:29,702 --> 00:33:31,702
How unfortunate. I'll be late for supper.
我现在有点饿了

281
00:33:31,702 --> 00:33:36,712
The restaurant downstairs will send up anything we want.
下面的餐厅可以送餐过来

282
00:33:36,712 --> 00:33:40,702
I'll go order something.
我可以帮你叫

283
00:33:53,722 --> 00:33:57,732
I have several ideas to improve the contents of your magazine.
那是杂志"彩虹"的创刊号

284
00:33:57,732 --> 00:34:02,732
For instance, one could - this is just one possibility -
我对此有很好的计划

285
00:34:02,732 --> 00:34:04,732
one could publish a play,
我们可以连载戏曲

286
00:34:04,732 --> 00:34:07,742
and on the facing pages show the characters
豪华的登场人物

287
00:34:07,742 --> 00:34:12,634
dressed in a certain way as if it were the fashion -
穿着最新流行的服装  在那里演绎故事

288
00:34:12,801 --> 00:34:16,972
the latest fashion, of course. One could also envision
我还有一个  正在准备中的计划

289
00:34:16,972 --> 00:34:23,687
other things, like, for example, publishing the works of Baudelaire
把波特里的生涯  写成连载怎么样

290
00:34:23,812 --> 00:34:25,855
in serial form -

291
00:34:38,772 --> 00:34:40,772
<i>When may I come for it?</i>
什么时候完成

292
00:34:40,772 --> 00:34:44,782
I'll finish it tomorrow and bring it to you.
明天早上我会送到府上

293
00:34:44,782 --> 00:34:50,171
I'd prefer to pay at once so as not to remain in debt to you.
我想拿到画之后再给你钱

294
00:34:50,782 --> 00:34:52,782
We're alike in that respect.
可以

295
00:34:52,782 --> 00:34:56,792
My cash is at the hotel. You'll have it tomorrow.
明天在酒店给你钱

296
00:34:56,792 --> 00:35:00,782
Now, if you'd get me my coat...
那我的上衣呢

297
00:35:11,802 --> 00:35:14,404
It was very dusty, so I had it laundered.
我已经洗干净了

298
00:35:14,404 --> 00:35:15,812
They only charged 40 francs.
洗衣服花了40法郎

299
00:35:15,812 --> 00:35:19,242
Just add it to my bill.
寄给我发票

300
00:35:41,832 --> 00:35:44,851
I'm not paying a thing!
不用给了

301
00:35:50,842 --> 00:35:52,832
Shit!
笨蛋

302
00:35:57,852 --> 00:35:59,824
The swine!
蠢猪

303
00:35:59,824 --> 00:36:02,744
He wanted to charge me
才走了几公里就叫我给钱

304
00:36:02,744 --> 00:36:04,704
for a few miles.
才走了几公里就叫我给钱

305
00:36:10,862 --> 00:36:13,862
There must be 60,000 francs there.
这里该有6万法郎吧

306
00:36:13,862 --> 00:36:15,872
15,240, to be precise -
正确的数字是1万5240法郎

307
00:36:15,872 --> 00:36:20,845
an advance for producing a sample issue of The Sash of Iris.
这是做  "彩虹"创刊编辑的订金

308
00:36:20,872 --> 00:36:22,872
Here's my plan.
我决定了

309
00:36:22,872 --> 00:36:25,767
Secure from life's material woes,
为了脱离贫困  我要拼命做事

310
00:36:25,767 --> 00:36:30,882
I intend to go about this seriously. First I'll get rid of these rags and dress decently
首先要买一套漂亮的衣服

311
00:36:30,882 --> 00:36:33,882
so that the fashion salons will take me seriously.
不能让他们小看我

312
00:36:33,882 --> 00:36:36,319
If you'll follow my example,
你们也这么做吧  做点关于广告的事情

313
00:36:36,319 --> 00:36:39,531
I can hire you as door-to-door ad salesmen.
他们马上会给你生活费

314
00:36:39,531 --> 00:36:43,451
Until then, let a strict economy govern our lives.
他们马上会给你生活费

315
00:36:43,892 --> 00:36:45,902
I accept wholeheartedly.
大家好好合作

316
00:36:45,902 --> 00:36:50,902
But to start with, give me a couple of thousand francs.
先给我2000～3000法郎

317
00:36:50,902 --> 00:36:51,902
Why?
为什么

318
00:36:51,902 --> 00:36:56,965
As a door-to-door salesman, I must have a car
要做广告就需要一辆车

319
00:36:57,912 --> 00:37:02,637
to call on potential advertisers in the provinces.
有时候也要到乡下  弄一些广告题材

320
00:37:02,912 --> 00:37:04,902
That's true.
没错

321
00:37:05,765 --> 00:37:07,922
Shall we order a table?
吃饭吧

322
00:37:07,922 --> 00:37:11,922
Yes. Then I can tell you more about my new job.
那边吃边说吧

323
00:37:11,922 --> 00:37:15,932
There's an excellent restaurant not far from here.
这附近有一个高级餐厅

324
00:37:15,932 --> 00:37:18,653
It's a bit expensive,
价格合理东西也好吃

325
00:37:18,653 --> 00:37:22,615
but we'll make it up in the time we save.
价格合理东西也好吃

326
00:37:22,932 --> 00:37:25,535
Very well, but starting tomorrow
只有今天晚上  明天开始要节约生活

327
00:37:25,535 --> 00:37:33,168
we shall devise even greater means of economizing. No more eating out. We'll hire a woman to cook for us.
取消在外面就餐  一切都在家里吃

328
00:37:33,952 --> 00:37:37,952
It would be wiser to take on a manservant who could then double as cook.
雇一个庸人  来给我们做饭就好了

329
00:37:37,952 --> 00:37:40,952
Our household would be in impeccable order
房子会变得很漂亮  而且也不贵

330
00:37:40,952 --> 00:37:43,962
and we'd have much more time to work
我们也可以专心做事

331
00:37:43,962 --> 00:37:47,962
with him to shine our shoes and see to our errands.
庸人会替你们擦好鞋子

332
00:37:47,962 --> 00:37:51,962
Then we'll need larger accommodations.
若那样就需要一个很大的房子

333
00:37:51,962 --> 00:37:54,731
That, in any case, is unavoidable
没错需要一个大点的楼房

334
00:37:54,731 --> 00:37:59,527
if we mean to live in keeping with our new position in society.
不能给我们的名声抹黑

335
00:38:04,982 --> 00:38:07,410
I'll be back.
我马上到

336
00:38:17,992 --> 00:38:21,090
A pack of Celtiques, please.
给我一箱酒

337
00:38:24,002 --> 00:38:28,389
Good evening, Mimi. You found work.
眯米找到事做了

338
00:38:29,002 --> 00:38:31,002
As you can see.
没错

339
00:38:31,002 --> 00:38:35,230
- And a place to live? - It comes with the job.
房子也找到了吗 有职工宿舍你们去酒吧吗

340
00:38:35,230 --> 00:38:41,012
Are you going to the nightclub? I just came along with my friends.
没有只是碰巧到这里而已

341
00:38:41,012 --> 00:38:43,738
I don't care for modern music.
虽然会喝酒  但我不喜欢嘈杂的音乐

342
00:38:43,738 --> 00:38:46,032
I'm going to have a drink.
虽然会喝酒  但我不喜欢嘈杂的音乐

343
00:38:49,022 --> 00:38:51,913
A glass of water, please.
给我杯水吧

344
00:39:12,042 --> 00:39:15,052
<i>- Who was that? - A regular.</i>
那个男人是 他是我们这里的常客

345
00:39:15,052 --> 00:39:19,042
He has the manners of a peasant.
看起来不怎么好

346
00:39:37,072 --> 00:39:39,711
It's kind of you to see me home,
你送我回去我很高兴  但我住的地方很远

347
00:39:39,711 --> 00:39:42,255
but this is nowhere near where I live.
你送我回去我很高兴  但我住的地方很远

348
00:39:45,082 --> 00:39:47,969
I wish you lived in Moscow
就算是莫斯科也没问题

349
00:39:47,969 --> 00:39:52,082
so I might have your company that much longer.
我想和你走到北的尽头

350
00:39:52,082 --> 00:39:54,642
That's a bit too far.
会很远的

351
00:39:56,092 --> 00:40:00,082
We could take the boulevard.
总会有到的时候

352
00:40:01,092 --> 00:40:03,276
Fancy that.
真难以置信

353
00:40:04,102 --> 00:40:08,092
We've arrived by chance where I live.
不知不觉到了我家了

354
00:40:09,102 --> 00:40:13,112
Wouldn't you like to come up and say hello to the dog?
你不想见到我的狗吗

355
00:40:13,112 --> 00:40:16,789
Very well, but just for a moment.
有一点

356
00:40:16,915 --> 00:40:19,112
I'll make some coffee.
我去趟咖啡厅

357
00:40:19,112 --> 00:40:23,671
In the meanwhile, you may enjoy the city view from my window.
期间从窗户欣赏街头景象吧

358
00:40:30,122 --> 00:40:32,132
They wilted.
已经枯萎了

359
00:40:32,132 --> 00:40:35,224
Had I known, I'd have bought
早知道买塑料花就好了

360
00:40:35,224 --> 00:40:37,018
plastic flowers.
早知道买塑料花就好了

361
00:40:42,142 --> 00:40:44,142
What's his name?
你的狗叫什么

362
00:40:44,142 --> 00:40:46,277
Baudelaire.
波特里

363
00:40:50,990 --> 00:40:53,368
I'm out of coffee,
你先喝咖啡我给你做汤

364
00:40:53,368 --> 00:40:55,411
but I'll make some soup.
你先喝咖啡我给你做汤

365
00:41:54,212 --> 00:41:58,202
May I kiss your hand?
我可以吻你的手吗

366
00:42:01,102 --> 00:42:03,222
You move fast.
你真性急

367
00:42:03,222 --> 00:42:07,212
The sooner to reach the goal.
你管善良的人这么说吗

368
00:42:49,262 --> 00:42:51,272
How much is this?
多少

369
00:42:51,272 --> 00:42:53,529
A hundred francs.
100法郎

370
00:42:55,031 --> 00:42:57,272
Fifty.
50

371
00:42:57,272 --> 00:43:00,161
All right. For you, 50.
拿走吧

372
00:43:06,282 --> 00:43:10,272
How about this?
不要领带吗

373
00:44:30,372 --> 00:44:33,372
I live with two other girls.
和另外两个女人一起住

374
00:44:33,372 --> 00:44:38,372
They have a male friend in common whom they're constantly fighting over.
她们两个为了一个男人  整天在吵架

375
00:44:38,372 --> 00:44:40,382
I don't get it.
我不觉得怎么样

376
00:44:40,382 --> 00:44:45,266
The man is stupid and ugly, and married to boot.
那个男人又蠢又丑陋  而且已经结婚了

377
00:44:45,382 --> 00:44:47,226
Uglier than me?
比我还丑陋吗

378
00:44:47,226 --> 00:44:51,392
There's no comparison. Next to him, you're Lino Ventura.
你跟他比起来  简直是个美男子

379
00:44:51,392 --> 00:44:52,392
Who's that?
是吗

380
00:44:52,392 --> 00:44:55,392
An Italian movie star. You don't know him?
你像意大利的名演员

381
00:44:55,392 --> 00:44:58,613
Forget him.
忘了意大利的演员  我有话和你说

382
00:44:58,613 --> 00:45:05,369
Let's talk about me. Why not... move in with me?
不想和我一起生活吗

383
00:45:06,287 --> 00:45:09,412
I'm against marriage in principle,
虽然我是单身主义者

384
00:45:09,412 --> 00:45:13,294
but we could make an exception.
但我喜欢和你在一起

385
00:45:13,294 --> 00:45:18,424
You'll stop working. I'll support us both with my paintings.
不要做事了  我卖画就可以维持生活

386
00:45:18,799 --> 00:45:22,345
And what would I do?
那我做什么

387
00:45:22,345 --> 00:45:26,307
You'd walk Baudelaire, clean the place -
带狗散步 还有打扫房间和其它家务

388
00:45:26,307 --> 00:45:28,142
that sort of thing.
做饭吗

389
00:45:28,142 --> 00:45:30,432
Are you serious?
不用

390
00:45:30,432 --> 00:45:32,432
I'll clean...
我会做

391
00:45:32,432 --> 00:45:36,432
and you can look out the window at the park.
你只要  从窗户看着公园就可以了

392
00:45:36,432 --> 00:45:40,432
In the evenings we'll go to the opera.
晚上可以到剧院看戏

393
00:45:58,462 --> 00:46:02,343
My wallet's been stolen.
我的钱包被偷了  你带钱了吗

394
00:46:02,343 --> 00:46:08,452
Do you have any money? Just a few francs.
我只有几法郎而已

395
00:46:30,492 --> 00:46:34,482
Police?
是警察局吗

396
00:46:38,502 --> 00:46:42,492
Your passport.
请出示身份证

397
00:46:56,512 --> 00:46:59,522
Listen, how much is their check?
是多少钱

398
00:46:59,522 --> 00:47:01,522
Four hundred twenty.
是420法郎

399
00:47:01,522 --> 00:47:04,522
Will you allow me to pay it?
让我来吧

400
00:47:04,522 --> 00:47:08,532
You think you'll get your money back from that burn?
他不会还你钱的

401
00:47:08,532 --> 00:47:11,203
It doesn't matter.
没关系

402
00:47:11,454 --> 00:47:14,790
Then as far as we're concerned, the matter is settled.
谢谢

403
00:47:20,421 --> 00:47:22,532
I have to go now.
不走了

404
00:47:23,382 --> 00:47:27,136
I start work at 9:00.
9点开始我要做事

405
00:47:27,136 --> 00:47:30,552
I have to wait for my passport.
我等他们还给我护照

406
00:47:30,552 --> 00:47:33,100
I'll come by your place tomorrow evening.
明晚见

407
00:47:34,552 --> 00:47:37,229
I'll be waiting.
等等

408
00:48:00,582 --> 00:48:02,582
Come with me.
过来

409
00:48:02,582 --> 00:48:04,582
Why?
为什么

410
00:48:04,582 --> 00:48:08,582
There's something suspicious about your papers.
有些不明的地方

411
00:48:13,592 --> 00:48:17,144
You've resided in France for three years with no visa,
没有护照却在法国  不法居留三年

412
00:48:17,144 --> 00:48:20,481
no residence permit, no work permit.
也没有劳动许可证

413
00:48:20,481 --> 00:48:23,609
You claim you came by train from Spain,
你说自己是从西班牙  坐汽车来的

414
00:48:23,609 --> 00:48:26,195
but you choose to say nothing more.
你说自己是从西班牙  坐汽车来的

415
00:48:27,612 --> 00:48:30,612
There is nothing more to say.
我没有那么说过

416
00:48:30,612 --> 00:48:32,612
Very well.
是吗

417
00:48:32,612 --> 00:48:35,538
You'll spend the night here.
关到拘留所

418
00:48:35,612 --> 00:48:39,667
We'll decide your fate in the morning.
明天早上再决定怎么处理

419
00:48:41,622 --> 00:48:43,796
May I make a call?
我想打电话家里只有狗

420
00:48:43,796 --> 00:48:47,622
My dog is home alone. - In the morning.
明天

421
00:49:32,672 --> 00:49:36,557
You're to be deported immediately to Albania.
坐两个小时候的航班  回阿尔巴尼亚

422
00:49:36,557 --> 00:49:42,354
The flight for Athens leaves in two hours. If you're found within France's borders again
若以后还到法国非法居留

423
00:49:42,354 --> 00:49:47,682
without the necessary papers, it will mean six months in jail.
就会让你坐6个月的牢

424
00:49:48,692 --> 00:49:51,692
May I make a call now?
我现在可以打电话了吗

425
00:49:51,692 --> 00:49:53,991
Make it fast.
要快点

426
00:50:00,702 --> 00:50:03,375
Mimi hasn't arrived yet.
眯米还没来

427
00:50:03,702 --> 00:50:05,920
I don't know.
没错

428
00:50:07,712 --> 00:50:11,702
Try again in a couple of hours.
过一会再打过来吧

429
00:50:13,594 --> 00:50:15,513
Morning, Henri.
刚有过你的电话

430
00:50:15,513 --> 00:50:16,722
- Someone just called for you. - Who?
是谁

431
00:50:16,722 --> 00:50:17,722
He didn't say.
不知道

432
00:50:17,722 --> 00:50:20,976
Could you make me a coffee?
给我咖啡

433
00:50:27,732 --> 00:50:29,732
马歇尔

434
00:50:29,732 --> 00:50:34,114
<i>Listen...</i> I'm being deported.
我被他们遣送回国了

435
00:50:34,732 --> 00:50:38,732
Will you look after Baudelaire and my paintings?
请收好波特里和我的画

436
00:50:39,742 --> 00:50:42,742
I won't be coming back.
我不会再回来

437
00:50:42,742 --> 00:50:47,127
They'll put me in jail if I do.
若以后再到法国就会蹲监狱

438
00:50:48,003 --> 00:50:49,129
Understand?

439
00:50:53,752 --> 00:50:55,742
Good-bye, Rodolfo.
保重

440
00:50:59,762 --> 00:51:01,762
- A Suze. - Problems?
里库尔 什么

441
00:51:01,762 --> 00:51:03,852
No. Just thirsty.
酒

442
00:51:37,802 --> 00:51:40,973
What do you think?
怎么样  我只花了1800法郎

443
00:51:40,973 --> 00:51:46,145
1,800 francs. Only 19,000 miles. It has brakes...
可以行驶2万公里  还有刹车也很好

444
00:51:47,438 --> 00:51:53,812
and everything. Great. Are you free this evening?
真不错今天晚上有空吗

445
00:51:53,812 --> 00:51:56,822
What's bothering you? You don't seem too enthusiastic.
你的脸色很难看怎么了

446
00:51:56,822 --> 00:52:00,822
Rodolfds been deported. No papers.
洛特勒夫要回国了

447
00:52:00,822 --> 00:52:01,822
Shit.
该死

448
00:52:01,822 --> 00:52:04,705
I'll go get Baudelaire.
我带走狗还有他的画要搬出来

449
00:52:04,705 --> 00:52:07,832
Let's meet there tonight and haul his paintings to your place.
我带走狗还有他的画要搬出来

450
00:52:07,832 --> 00:52:09,822
All right.
知道了

451
00:52:30,852 --> 00:52:33,233
Evening, ma'am.
晚上好

452
00:52:52,872 --> 00:52:54,872
- Are you looking for Rodolfo? - Yes.
你找谁

453
00:52:54,872 --> 00:52:59,760
We were to meet here. Where is he?
是的我们约好见面  他在哪里

454
00:53:00,094 --> 00:53:02,882
He's been deported. He was in the country illegally.
因为非法居留  所以被遣送回国了

455
00:53:02,882 --> 00:53:03,882
When?
什么时候

456
00:53:03,882 --> 00:53:05,892
This afternoon.
今天下午

457
00:53:05,892 --> 00:53:08,268
Is he coming back?
还回来吗

458
00:53:08,892 --> 00:53:10,882
I don't know.
不知道

459
00:53:11,814 --> 00:53:15,892
I have to go. Shut the door when you leave.
好了走吧  出来的时候把窗户关好

460
00:53:45,802 --> 00:53:48,976
SPRING
春天

461
00:54:43,739 --> 00:54:46,872
Hello, Musette. How's it going?
穆杰多你还好吗

462
00:54:46,872 --> 00:54:49,119
What's it look like?
老样子

463
00:54:50,872 --> 00:54:54,872
How many today? We have to go to press Friday.
广告有了吗  周五之前要印刷好

464
00:54:54,872 --> 00:54:58,879
Just one, but a full page. For Printemps.
找到了一件  是"佛朗坦"的一面广告

465
00:54:58,879 --> 00:55:01,882
I know. They called and cancelled it.
那个广告就取消吧

466
00:55:01,882 --> 00:55:06,720
Coffee originated in Arabia, where it was discovered by a goat.
阿拉伯原产咖啡  是被亚奇发现的

467
00:55:06,845 --> 00:55:10,892
Balzac drank 70 cups a day.
巴尔扎克一天会喝70多杯

468
00:55:10,892 --> 00:55:14,892
What are you up to with that ladder?
那个梯子是什么

469
00:55:14,892 --> 00:55:17,981
It's the link between me and my beloved.
这是连接我和我爱人的桥梁

470
00:55:17,981 --> 00:55:22,902
Have you read Shakespeare? Of course. He was a great philosopher.
知道了你这个大哲学家

471
00:55:22,902 --> 00:55:26,912
Do you remember <i>Romeo and Juliet?</i>
"罗米欧和朱丽叶"怎么样

472
00:55:26,912 --> 00:55:28,912
Do I remember it?
歇尔夫...

473
00:55:28,912 --> 00:55:32,120
“It was the nightingale and not the lark
"弄醒你的不是画眉鸟"

474
00:55:32,120 --> 00:55:35,912
that pierced the fearful hollow of thine ear.”
"是耐辛盖尔"

475
00:55:35,912 --> 00:55:38,627
Don't you understand?
就那样

476
00:55:38,922 --> 00:55:40,922
I've met a girl from a good family,
我认识了一个大家闺秀

477
00:55:40,922 --> 00:55:45,092
but for certain reasons her father can't stand me
她的父亲憎恨我  甚至想杀了我

478
00:55:45,259 --> 00:55:49,638
and has threatened to kill me. The girl's name is Juliette,
她叫朱丽叶家里还有舞台

479
00:55:49,638 --> 00:55:52,766
and her room just happens to have a balcony.
她叫朱丽叶家里还有舞台

480
00:55:52,891 --> 00:55:55,602
I came to borrow this bird
改天晚上借我这只小鸟

481
00:55:55,602 --> 00:55:59,942
to wake me every morning before the old man gets up.
是为了第二天早上  比她父亲早起

482
00:55:59,942 --> 00:56:04,278
I'd be obliged if from now on you'd call me
今天开始 叫我做罗米欧

483
00:56:04,278 --> 00:56:10,942
Romeo Montague. What do you think of my plan?
太罗嗦了吧

484
00:56:12,952 --> 00:56:16,962
<i>The Sash of Iris,</i> hello.
这里是"彩虹"编辑部

485
00:56:16,962 --> 00:56:20,952
It's for you, Marcel, from abroad.
是一个外国人

486
00:56:24,962 --> 00:56:26,962
All right.
你好

487
00:56:27,972 --> 00:56:29,970
Where?
哪里

488
00:56:30,972 --> 00:56:32,962
What time?
几点

489
00:56:34,972 --> 00:56:36,972
Very well.
知道了

490
00:56:37,982 --> 00:56:39,982
Forget about your Juliette. We have to go.
忘了你的恋人吧走

491
00:56:39,982 --> 00:56:40,982
- Where? - The border.
去哪里

492
00:56:40,982 --> 00:56:44,972
I'll explain on the way.
是边境后面再跟你解释

493
00:56:46,992 --> 00:56:49,992
Let me have a few hundred. - There is no money.
先借我 没有

494
00:56:49,992 --> 00:56:51,992
Where did it all go?
我看你有

495
00:56:51,992 --> 00:56:54,870
I paid the printer so they'd give me the magazines.
印刷的时候用完了

496
00:56:54,870 --> 00:56:56,997
You could have left them there.
那也会有一点

497
00:56:56,997 --> 00:57:00,992
We need a picture for the cover.
我还要照相呢

498
00:57:09,593 --> 00:57:12,002
Hold still.
别动

499
00:57:19,811 --> 00:57:21,396
Now let's go.

500
00:58:12,072 --> 00:58:14,062
There he is.
是他

501
00:58:47,112 --> 00:58:51,111
Shall we go? We can make Paris by morning.
我想马上跑到巴黎

502
01:00:51,232 --> 01:00:54,442
- When is Mimi in? - Mimi isn't here anymore.
眯米在吗 她已经不干了  但每天晚上都会过来玩

503
01:00:54,442 --> 01:00:57,070
But they stop in almost every evening.
眯米在吗 她已经不干了  但每天晚上都会过来玩

504
01:00:57,237 --> 01:00:58,242
Who's “they”?
和什么人一起

505
01:00:58,242 --> 01:01:02,232
Mimi and Francis, her boyfriend. Why do you ask?
和她的情人佛朗希斯一起  有什么事吗

506
01:01:02,909 --> 01:01:07,664
I'm an old friend. Thank you.
她是我的老朋友

507
01:01:52,834 --> 01:01:54,302
Good evening.
晚上好

508
01:01:54,302 --> 01:01:55,302
How are you? - Fine.
还好吗

509
01:01:55,302 --> 01:01:58,302
Someone was asking for you. - Who?
是啊你的朋友来了 谁

510
01:01:58,302 --> 01:02:02,292
An old friend. He's sitting over there.
是你的老朋友在那边

511
01:03:25,392 --> 01:03:30,140
I believe The Crossing of the Red Sea
眯米 "红海横断"  这幅画已经完成了

512
01:03:30,140 --> 01:03:33,402
is finished. I feel empty.
但我不会卖

513
01:03:33,402 --> 01:03:38,273
If you manage to sell it, we can pay the rent.
现在卖了才会有钱交租

514
01:03:38,402 --> 01:03:42,412
Perhaps you could come down on the price.
便宜点卖吧

515
01:03:42,412 --> 01:03:45,572
I won't sell it for less
200法郎以下我不会卖的

516
01:03:45,572 --> 01:03:49,909
than 200 francs. I've already put
为了画这幅画  我花了1万法郎以上

517
01:03:49,909 --> 01:03:55,540
over 10,000 francs' worth of paint into it. What if the landlord calls the police?
我担心你会被警察抓走

518
01:03:55,540 --> 01:03:58,335
You still don't have a residence permit.
我担心你会被警察抓走

519
01:03:59,711 --> 01:04:02,422
Come in.
请进

520
01:04:16,442 --> 01:04:18,442
What a surprise.
真令人吃惊

521
01:04:18,442 --> 01:04:20,432
眯米

522
01:04:21,608 --> 01:04:26,442
Would you offer our guest a glass of water?
给客人倒一杯水吧

523
01:04:28,452 --> 01:04:30,462
To what do I owe this honor?
有事吗

524
01:04:30,462 --> 01:04:33,203
I was so inspired by your portrait
我喜欢上油画  现在变成了收藏家

525
01:04:33,203 --> 01:04:39,452
that I've decided to become a collector. I'm now looking for a relatively large painting,
我想现在就要一幅大画

526
01:04:39,793 --> 01:04:43,630
and I thought of you. You're in luck.
这幅画刚画好

527
01:04:43,630 --> 01:04:47,472
I just finished this one and intended to send it off
和其它的作品一起

528
01:04:47,472 --> 01:04:49,472
in the morning with some other works
明天早上要送走

529
01:04:49,472 --> 01:04:53,482
to an exhibition in New York.
在纽约开展览会

530
01:04:53,482 --> 01:04:56,482
But if you'd care to make an offer...
但也可以出售

531
01:04:56,482 --> 01:05:00,492
as an old customer...
你是不错的买主

532
01:05:00,492 --> 01:05:03,492
I like the work very much.
是个不错的作品

533
01:05:03,492 --> 01:05:06,492
I'll give you 1,000 francs.
1000法郎怎么样

534
01:05:06,492 --> 01:05:09,197
- You're joking. - 1,200.
太便宜了 1200法郎

535
01:05:09,197 --> 01:05:10,490
2,000.
2000法郎

536
01:05:10,490 --> 01:05:11,502
1,400.
1400法郎

537
01:05:11,502 --> 01:05:13,502
1,700.
1700法郎

538
01:05:13,502 --> 01:05:17,502
1,500...
1500法郎

539
01:05:17,502 --> 01:05:21,502
and two tickets to the opera this evening.
再给你两张演出入场券

540
01:05:22,512 --> 01:05:26,502
Opera is a dying art form, but all right.
虽然那些都是腐烂的艺术  但也好

541
01:05:45,532 --> 01:05:49,542
Go pay the rent and then get dressed.
交了房租之后要买点衣服

542
01:05:49,542 --> 01:05:53,532
You and Musette can go to the opera.
我们到剧院看戏

543
01:05:57,542 --> 01:05:59,873
I'll wait outside.
我到外面和马歇尔见面

544
01:06:00,498 --> 01:06:03,042
I have to talk to Marcel.

545
01:06:58,602 --> 01:07:01,351
Poor girls.
强迫女人过贫穷的生活  太残酷了

546
01:07:01,351 --> 01:07:04,229
They were never meant to live like this.
强迫女人过贫穷的生活  太残酷了

547
01:07:04,612 --> 01:07:08,622
Being men, and thus stronger in every respect,
但男人很强大

548
01:07:08,622 --> 01:07:11,622
we bear up joyfully under every misfortune.
就算遭受挫折也不会气馁

549
01:07:11,622 --> 01:07:13,821
We don't sink into depression
每天穿着睡衣也可以生活

550
01:07:13,821 --> 01:07:16,622
if our outfit isn't always neat and tidy.
每天穿着睡衣也可以生活

551
01:07:16,622 --> 01:07:20,632
But for women it's different.
但女人这样可不行

552
01:07:20,632 --> 01:07:24,632
The simplest frock brings them joy, and one can't fault them for that.
为一件衣服欢欣鼓舞的就是女人

553
01:07:24,632 --> 01:07:27,293
On the other hand,
最近美术或者  文化市场开始有了活力

554
01:07:27,293 --> 01:07:31,548
the market for art and literature has been bustling recently.
最近美术或者  文化市场开始有了活力

555
01:07:32,642 --> 01:07:35,134
We'll soon be earning
我们也在东站附近租一个地方

556
01:07:35,134 --> 01:07:38,652
nearly as much as porters at the Gare de L'Est.
我们也在东站附近租一个地方

557
01:07:38,652 --> 01:07:40,652
It's true.
没错

558
01:07:40,652 --> 01:07:44,561
Works of art are selling like pancakes.
卖艺术品是好主意

559
01:07:44,561 --> 01:07:45,652
Then it's agreed.
就因为如此

560
01:07:45,652 --> 01:07:49,662
Tomorrow we take the girls shopping to indulge their feminine whims.
明天带女朋友去购物

561
01:07:49,662 --> 01:07:53,653
Sunday we'll go on a picnic in the countryside.
星期天到乡下玩

562
01:07:54,662 --> 01:07:55,662
What about me?
我呢

563
01:07:55,662 --> 01:07:58,672
You have two days to find yourself a companion.
到周日之前弄一个恋人出来

564
01:07:58,672 --> 01:08:02,672
It's not our fault if your appearance sparks no interest in the opposite sex.
你连喜欢的女人都没找到

565
01:08:02,672 --> 01:08:06,374
But if you have no luck, you can still come along...
没找到也要来你当司机

566
01:08:06,374 --> 01:08:08,042
as our driver.
没找到也要来你当司机

567
01:08:09,682 --> 01:08:14,048
Monsieur, there's a call for you in the kitchen.
有电话找你

568
01:08:15,216 --> 01:08:20,346
Madame... your eyes are like two moons.
夫人  你的眼镜就像月亮一样美丽

569
01:08:33,693 --> 01:08:37,692
Let's hope it doesn't come to more than 600 francs.
都是廉价商品也好

570
01:09:21,752 --> 01:09:23,742
波特里

571
01:11:06,679 --> 01:11:08,852
And never come back!
扔掉吧

572
01:11:10,516 --> 01:11:12,862
They didn't like it?
不行吗

573
01:11:12,862 --> 01:11:15,188
Idiots!
像傻瓜一样

574
01:11:15,563 --> 01:11:17,872
They tried to discourage me.
没有长眼睛

575
01:11:17,872 --> 01:11:21,360
They said I should break my brushes in two
但我不会折断笔  然后再自杀

576
01:11:21,360 --> 01:11:23,696
and jump out the window.
但我不会折断笔  然后再自杀

577
01:11:26,882 --> 01:11:30,077
Let's go borrow some money from Marcel
跟马歇尔借点钱吃点什么吧

578
01:11:30,077 --> 01:11:32,288
and go out to eat.
跟马歇尔借点钱吃点什么吧

579
01:11:48,554 --> 01:11:50,431
I gave you
我给你们钱

580
01:11:50,431 --> 01:11:53,392
a cash advance.
我给你们钱

581
01:11:54,902 --> 01:11:57,772
I want it back
两天之内一定要还给我

582
01:11:57,772 --> 01:12:01,400
in two days. Not three or five.
只有两天

583
01:12:01,567 --> 01:12:06,072
Two days. Good luck...
已经结束了

584
01:12:06,922 --> 01:12:08,912
and good-bye.
再见

585
01:12:15,922 --> 01:12:17,922
一群白痴

586
01:12:26,592 --> 01:12:27,942
What was that all about?
为什么关门了

587
01:12:27,942 --> 01:12:31,264
He's mad that I serialized my play.
我的连载不合他们的脾胃

588
01:12:31,264 --> 01:12:35,768
Says it didn't suit the magazine's style and that readers complained.
他们完全不考虑读者的心情

589
01:12:35,768 --> 01:12:40,940
What readers? Besides, as editor in chief, I set the style.
决定编辑方针的是我

590
01:12:40,940 --> 01:12:42,952
He was just the publisher. Capitalist!
那个资本主义家伙

591
01:12:42,952 --> 01:12:45,952
- I'm hungry. - Me too.
肚子饿了 我也是

592
01:12:45,952 --> 01:12:48,698
Come eat at my place.
在家里吃吧

593
01:12:48,865 --> 01:12:50,962
I happen to have a little money.
我有东西吃

594
01:12:50,962 --> 01:12:56,080
While we're at it, I can play my latest composition for you.
顺便可以给你们听我的新曲

595
01:15:01,092 --> 01:15:03,082
你被逮捕了

596
01:15:30,109 --> 01:15:34,122
I'm going to leave Marcel.
我要离开马歇尔

597
01:15:34,122 --> 01:15:35,132
When?
什么时候

598
01:15:35,132 --> 01:15:37,575
Tonight.
今天晚上

599
01:15:38,132 --> 01:15:42,132
I've already packed.
我已经收拾好了

600
01:15:42,132 --> 01:15:44,665
Does he know?
他怎么说

601
01:15:47,142 --> 01:15:49,420
I didn't dare tell him.
不知道

602
01:15:51,922 --> 01:15:56,152
I'm going back to Strasbourg. There's this farmer there.
回到故乡和富翁结婚

603
01:15:56,152 --> 01:16:00,142
He's not great-looking, but he's sweet...
就算长得不帅  只要慈祥又真心就可以了

604
01:16:00,222 --> 01:16:01,932
and dependable.

605
01:16:03,152 --> 01:16:07,063
Why?
那马歇尔怎么办

606
01:16:07,063 --> 01:16:09,152
Marcel doesn't need me.
不需要我

607
01:16:12,162 --> 01:16:15,863
All he loves is his books.
对他来说书就是全部

608
01:16:15,863 --> 01:16:19,172
Yesterday I pawned my ring for rent money.
我为了房租连戒指都当进去了

609
01:16:19,172 --> 01:16:23,621
I left the money on the table. When I came back, he'd taken it...
他就用那个钱全都买书看

610
01:16:24,182 --> 01:16:27,182
and spent it all on first-edition Balzacs.
而且买的是巴尔扎克的书

611
01:16:27,182 --> 01:16:29,210
Poor Marcel.
可怜的男人

612
01:16:31,182 --> 01:16:34,256
He'll forget me in a week.
别忘了我

613
01:16:35,192 --> 01:16:39,512
In any case, quicker than I'll forget him.
不知不觉间

614
01:16:42,192 --> 01:16:46,202
That's how men are.
男人都是薄情的

615
01:16:46,202 --> 01:16:48,202
Will you see me to the station? - Of course.
送我去车站吧

616
01:16:48,202 --> 01:16:51,202
I'll miss you.
当然我会很寂寞的

617
01:16:51,202 --> 01:16:53,202
You must come visit!
来见我

618
01:16:53,202 --> 01:16:55,861
I'll send you the fare.
我会给你车费如果是富翁  那肯定很有钱

619
01:16:55,861 --> 01:16:59,782
The man's rich. I promise.
我一定去

620
01:17:00,212 --> 01:17:02,660
Write to me care of general delivery.
要给我写信

621
01:17:02,993 --> 01:17:06,222
Why general delivery?
你要分手吗

622
01:17:06,222 --> 01:17:08,212
I don't know.
不知道

623
01:17:30,242 --> 01:17:33,252
开往斯特拉斯夫的列车

624
01:17:33,252 --> 01:17:37,242
马上就要发车了  乘客请上车

625
01:18:13,292 --> 01:18:15,292
How's it going, Mimi?
你还好吗

626
01:18:15,292 --> 01:18:17,292
Fine.
是的

627
01:18:17,292 --> 01:18:19,282
Can I give you a ride?
坐上来吧

628
01:18:20,292 --> 01:18:23,365
You can drive me home.
送我回家吧

629
01:18:43,322 --> 01:18:46,322
Yes, darling.
洛特勒夫 你想怎么样

630
01:18:46,322 --> 01:18:48,682
I found work.
我要工作

631
01:18:50,322 --> 01:18:52,332
You needn't have.
没必要工作

632
01:18:52,332 --> 01:18:56,273
I can't go on living like this, never having any money.
我无法忍受贫穷的生活

633
01:18:56,273 --> 01:18:58,332
I can't breathe. It's like I'm suffocating.
我快无法呼吸了

634
01:18:58,332 --> 01:19:01,332
I'll open the window.
要我开窗户吗

635
01:19:01,332 --> 01:19:06,033
That won't help. Besides, it's already cold in here.
傻瓜是为了家计才这样

636
01:19:06,342 --> 01:19:10,342
Shall I light a fire in the stove?
我给你开暖炉吧

637
01:19:10,342 --> 01:19:13,499
There's no wood or coal.
没有燃料

638
01:19:24,362 --> 01:19:26,595
Some old poems of mine.
这是我的诗

639
01:19:27,304 --> 01:19:30,933
I thought I'd publish a collection...
我一直想出自己的诗集

640
01:19:30,933 --> 01:19:32,559
someday.
我一直想出自己的诗集

641
01:19:54,392 --> 01:19:59,211
At least they'll provide some heat.
你会多少感到温暖

642
01:20:02,402 --> 01:20:04,717
I'm going for a little walk.
我去散散心

643
01:20:07,402 --> 01:20:10,556
Don't be too long.
早点回来

644
01:21:48,502 --> 01:21:50,512
Hello, Rodolfo.
洛特勒夫

645
01:21:50,512 --> 01:21:52,533
Hello, Mimi.
眯米

646
01:21:53,512 --> 01:21:58,122
I love you, you know, but life is hard.
虽然我爱你  但无法忍受贫穷的生活

647
01:21:59,512 --> 01:22:02,793
Yes. I understand.
我很清楚

648
01:22:28,861 --> 01:22:30,863
<i>I drink.</i>

649
01:22:31,196 --> 01:22:33,615
<i>Glass after glass</i>

650
01:22:34,867 --> 01:22:39,079
<i>To forget all about my wife's friends</i>

651
01:22:41,748 --> 01:22:44,418
<i>I drink.</i>

652
01:22:44,543 --> 01:22:46,879
<i>Glass after glass</i>

653
01:22:48,505 --> 01:22:53,844
<i>To forget all my troubles</i>

654
01:22:55,345 --> 01:22:57,806
<i>I drink.</i>

655
01:22:58,182 --> 01:23:01,018
<i>Any old swill</i>

656
01:23:02,060 --> 01:23:07,357
<i>As long as it's strong</i>

657
01:23:08,692 --> 01:23:10,986
<i>I drink.</i>

658
01:23:11,445 --> 01:23:13,822
<i>The cheapest stuff</i>

659
01:23:15,324 --> 01:23:17,576
<i>It's rough</i>

660
01:23:17,743 --> 01:23:20,454
<i>But it passes the time</i>

661
01:23:22,372 --> 01:23:25,417
<i>Is life really such a lark?</i>

662
01:23:25,667 --> 01:23:28,921
<i>Is it really so exciting?</i>

663
01:23:29,046 --> 01:23:32,716
<i>I ask</i>

664
01:23:32,841 --> 01:23:36,602
<i>Those two questions</i> AUTUMN
秋天

665
01:23:36,720 --> 01:23:38,931
<i>Is it worth living?</i>

666
01:23:39,306 --> 01:23:42,684
<i>Or loving, only to be cheated on?</i>

667
01:23:42,809 --> 01:23:45,938
<i>I ask those two questions</i>

668
01:23:47,606 --> 01:23:51,360
<i>But no one ever answers</i>

669
01:23:51,485 --> 01:23:54,238
<i>And so I drink</i>

670
01:23:54,363 --> 01:23:56,615
<i>Glass after glass</i>

671
01:24:10,652 --> 01:24:12,652
What?
怎么样

672
01:24:12,652 --> 01:24:14,642
Nothing.
没什么

673
01:24:32,150 --> 01:24:34,662
It's very good.
真不错

674
01:24:37,672 --> 01:24:41,785
The voice of the people is the voice of God.
人声就是天籁

675
01:24:41,785 --> 01:24:46,092
EVEN MOSES USED BLANCHERON SUGAR
佛朗修罗砂糖公司

676
01:24:51,402 --> 01:24:53,402
That there is known as turkey with truffles.
你们看

677
01:24:53,402 --> 01:24:56,550
火鸟料理已经结束了

678
01:24:56,550 --> 01:24:59,412
Look at the color of that leg of lamb!
还有烤得热烘烘的羊羔

679
01:24:59,412 --> 01:25:02,264
Lamb is the favorite food of the gods
是桑德拉夫人非常喜欢的东西

680
01:25:02,264 --> 01:25:05,183
and also of my godmother, Madame Chandlier.
是桑德拉夫人非常喜欢的东西

681
01:25:06,412 --> 01:25:10,439
And what about those trout? They're superb swimmers.
还有这个鳟鱼  这家伙可是游泳名将

682
01:25:10,832 --> 01:25:13,525
They climb rapids as quickly
如果有人请我们去吃晚餐  我们会比它更快

683
01:25:13,525 --> 01:25:16,842
as we'd accept an invitation to dinner this evening.
如果有人请我们去吃晚餐  我们会比它更快

684
01:25:16,842 --> 01:25:19,197
That fruit is known as pineapple.
还有菠萝

685
01:25:19,842 --> 01:25:23,035
I almost got to taste one once.
我吃过一次

686
01:25:23,852 --> 01:25:26,204
Speaking of fruit,
果实也可以但也不想失去肉

687
01:25:26,204 --> 01:25:32,753
I wouldn't say no to that pheasant there. Why this profusion of delicacies?
为什么会走这么快

688
01:25:32,753 --> 01:25:34,862
You don't know? It's All Saints' Day,
不知道吗

689
01:25:34,862 --> 01:25:39,217
a great family celebration.
今天是家人  都团聚在一起的圣诞节

690
01:25:39,843 --> 01:25:43,872
Would you care to spend the evening with me?
我们也庆祝吧

691
01:25:43,872 --> 01:25:44,872
No money.
没有钱

692
01:25:44,872 --> 01:25:47,643
How much have you got?
有多少

693
01:26:28,912 --> 01:26:31,728
I don't understand. I've lost my appetite.
我没有食欲

694
01:26:34,439 --> 01:26:36,912
Same here.
我也是

695
01:26:38,922 --> 01:26:40,932
I can see
我可以看到

696
01:26:40,932 --> 01:26:45,742
that a phantom from the past sits at this table.
过去的亡灵正坐在台上

697
01:26:45,932 --> 01:26:50,932
But if you intend to waste away to nothing,
如果有勇气饿死

698
01:26:50,932 --> 01:26:54,932
you could do so just as well on a full stomach.
也可以吃饱撑死

699
01:27:09,558 --> 01:27:12,894
Am I disturbing you?
妨碍你们了吗

700
01:27:12,894 --> 01:27:14,952
Come in.
进来吧

701
01:27:24,823 --> 01:27:26,962
I'm so cold.
真冷啊

702
01:27:27,826 --> 01:27:29,972
I happened to be passing by
走在路上

703
01:27:29,972 --> 01:27:33,982
and saw the light in the window.
可以看到窗户里的灯光

704
01:27:33,982 --> 01:27:37,753
I lost my apartment a week ago,
上周我被赶出来

705
01:27:37,753 --> 01:27:40,982
and I've been wandering the streets ever since.
在街上流浪了

706
01:27:40,982 --> 01:27:44,009
I'm posing for artists these days,
也当过模特  但也赚不到多少钱

707
01:27:44,009 --> 01:27:46,011
but it doesn't pay much.
也当过模特  但也赚不到多少钱

708
01:27:46,992 --> 01:27:50,982
Oh, I only show my face and hands.
只是手和脸的模特

709
01:27:52,642 --> 01:27:56,002
They've promised to pay me tomorrow.
明天我可以拿到钱

710
01:27:56,002 --> 01:27:59,992
Then I'll move back into my apartment.
我想回到家里

711
01:28:08,012 --> 01:28:11,022
- Where are you two going? - To get some cigars.
去哪里 去买雪茄

712
01:28:11,022 --> 01:28:12,022
In Havana.
一直到巴西

713
01:28:12,022 --> 01:28:14,706
We'll be back tomorrow
我们明天早上会回来

714
01:28:14,706 --> 01:28:17,292
sure as arrows loosed by a steady hand.
我们明天早上会回来

715
01:28:30,889 --> 01:28:32,808
Where have you been?
你一直呆在哪里了

716
01:28:32,808 --> 01:28:36,042
Don't ask any questions.
什么也别问了

717
01:28:36,042 --> 01:28:39,648
Just let me sit here by your side.
我想留在你身边  这里是温暖的

718
01:28:39,648 --> 01:28:41,733
It's so warm here.
我想留在你身边  这里是温暖的

719
01:28:43,860 --> 01:28:47,052
I'll stay until tomorrow. All right?
我能和你在一起吗

720
01:28:47,052 --> 01:28:49,991
It's going to be very cold here.
这里很冷

721
01:28:50,052 --> 01:28:52,062
Good.
好吧

722
01:28:52,062 --> 01:28:56,062
It'll be just like before.
真像以前一样

723
01:28:56,062 --> 01:28:58,750
I'll clear the table.
我来收拾吧

724
01:29:03,072 --> 01:29:07,759
The warmth has made me dizzy. I can hardly stand up.
因为热所以头都晕了  站不起来

725
01:29:14,082 --> 01:29:16,351
You have a fever.
你发烧

726
01:29:16,977 --> 01:29:21,072
I'll help you into bed.
我带你到床上躺下

727
01:30:17,142 --> 01:30:21,152
Schaunard and I will go get a doctor.
我和肖纳罗去叫医生

728
01:30:21,152 --> 01:30:25,211
You stay here and keep Mimi company.
帮我照顾眯米

729
01:30:44,172 --> 01:30:47,943
I was awake the whole time.
他一直都没睡觉

730
01:30:47,943 --> 01:30:50,182
Rodolfo still loves me.
他还爱着我

731
01:30:50,182 --> 01:30:52,182
What about you?
你呢

732
01:30:52,182 --> 01:30:54,658
I never stopped loving him.
我也爱他

733
01:30:54,783 --> 01:30:56,182
Then all is well.
太好了

734
01:30:56,182 --> 01:31:00,872
I'm going away forever.
但我要去远行

735
01:31:01,998 --> 01:31:04,182
What are you talking about?
什么意思

736
01:31:05,192 --> 01:31:07,379
I'm going to die soon.
我马上会死

737
01:31:08,129 --> 01:31:10,192
Look.
你看

